    Serializable, Iterable, DomainObject

    public class DomainLeafNode
extends DomainLeafNode_Base
    LeafNode specialized to hold a mapping of [Oid, DomainObject] The serialization of DomainLeafNode is done using a JSON array, containing the External Id of the stored objects.
